## Import



GaussDB instance can be imported using the instance `id`, e.g.

```sh
 $ pulumi import huaweicloud:GaussDB/mysqlProxy:MysqlProxy proxy_1 ee678f40-ce8e-4d0c-8221-38dead426f06
```
